Booking.com

Full time / Part time position: Property Manager


 

Objective
The goal of this project is to onboard Joel as a Property Manager and ensure the successful listing and management of properties on the Booking.com platform. The focus will be on efficient property setup, account management, and seamless customer service to facilitate smooth operations and guest bookings.
 

Scope of Work​

  1. Mobile App Setup

    • Download and install the Booking App on a mobile device.

  2. Access Property Information

    • Retrieve essential property information from the Notepad (.txt) file provided, and download the property images from the linked Google Drive folder.

  3. Platform Registration

    • Register on www.booking.com as a host.

    • For Booking.com, list the property under Profile > List your property

  4. Account Setup

    • Set up an account with a personal email and phone number.

  5. Property Listings Creation

    • Publish the property on Booking.com by following platform guidelines.

    • On Booking.com, select the option for guests to be charged at the property and enable Instant Booking.

  6. Property Management

    • Manage property inquiries, bookings, and availability updates across the platform. Ensure timely responses to potential guests.

  7. Forwarding Guest Information

    • Collect and forward guest reservation details (including name, email, phone number, booking period, and payment info) in PDF format to the company.

  8. Timeline and Submission

    • All tasks, including property registration and publication, must be completed and submitted within 48 hours.

    • Property listing link will be sent to the company for verification.
       

Deliverables​

  • Completed registration and live property listings on Booking.com.

  • Guest information and booking details forwarded to the company in a timely manner.

  • Verification of property links upon listing completion.
     

Support​

The candidate will receive support from the team throughout the project, ensuring that any issues encountered during registration, listing, or management can be resolved swiftly.
 

Expected Outcome
By the end of the task, the property will be live and available for bookings on Booking.com platform. This will ensure a strong start for the candidate's role as Property Manager, allowing for efficient management and maximized bookings.
